                <p>Want to contribute? Check out our contributing guidelines:</p>
                <p><a href="https://github.com/theatrus/tenrankai/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Contributing Guide</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="community-section">
            <h3>Community Guidelines</h3>
